				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6048679#post-4371509</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6048679/scp-3727#post-4371509</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2019 01:38:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jim North</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2191727</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like it. Aside from it being an interesting ability, I really like how UNinterested the guy himself is in his new ability. Pulling syringes out of the walls in the same manner someone would idly chew on their fingernails or drum their fingers on a table strikes me as particularly comical.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
